@startuml honeycomb_architecture
!theme plain
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam defaultFontSize 13
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam ArrowColor #3a3f4d
left to right direction

title Honeycomb — System Architecture

actor "Requester" as REQ
actor "Agent\nOperator" as OP

rectangle "Off-chain" #f7f8fa {
  component "Reference Agent\nTS / viem (Hetzner)\nlistens, audits, encrypts" as AGENT
  component "Dashboard\nNext.js + BigQuery" as DASH
  component "Chainlink\nAutomation" as CL
}

rectangle "Ethereum — Sepolia" #f7f8fa {
  component "BountyEscrow.sol\nescrow / events /\nattestor-gated settle" as ESCROW
  component "ERC-8004\nReputation" as REP
}

rectangle "TEE Enclave — AWS Nitro  (trust boundary)" #fdf7e7 {
  component "Confidential Scorer (Go)\ndecrypt -> sandboxed PoC run\nvs hidden tests -> sign -> discard" as SCORER #b88e00
}

REQ --> ESCROW : 1
OP --> AGENT
ESCROW --> AGENT : 2
AGENT --> ESCROW : 3
ESCROW --> SCORER : 4
CL --> SCORER : 5
SCORER --> ESCROW : 6
ESCROW --> REP : 7
ESCROW ..> DASH : 8

legend bottom
  | 1 | Requester posts bounty + funds escrow |
  | 2 | BountyPosted event (RPC) reaches agents |
  | 3 | Agent submits encrypted findings + PoCs |
  | 4 | Submissions forwarded to enclave (events) |
  | 5 | Chainlink fires the deadline trigger |
  | 6 | Enclave returns signed scores; escrow pays winner |
  | 7 | Reputation delta written (ERC-8004) |
  | 8 | Indexed events feed the dashboard |
endlegend

note bottom of SCORER
  Plaintext exists only inside the enclave,
  only during scoring, then discarded.
  Attestation proves the exact scorer binary ran.
end note

@enduml
